    "name": "MahTank Model.1942",
    "gameVersion": "0.2.50.10",
    "mass": 20446,
    "creationDate": "1943.12.31",
    "class": "",
    "desc": "A new design standard was implemented in early 1942 for improved riveting techniques. The first design using the new methods was model 1942, a smaller conventional design with a rather large cannon fitted to make up Groent's lacking proficiency in offensive technologies. Even though this was supposed to mostly serve as a testbed for new construction methods, it became the preferred vehicle among tank crews, beginning the later turn away from tank doctrine.",
